     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                                Test05
                                ------

  The purpose of this test is to exercise the G4TessellatedSolid class and 
  its related surface types (triangular and quadrangular surface) forming a
  combined G4 geometry made by facets. It also exercises the General Particle
  Source framework.

  Author: Fan Lei
  Contributors: Gabriele Cosmo

  To run it you can use:

    test05 test05.in
